OL,3,CCouple's dazzling Christmas lights in
OL,4,Cmemory of son raises thousands for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FA couple from Kent who spread joy
OL,8,Fevery Christmas with enchanting light
OL,9,Fdisplays.
OL,11,FEvery year Ross and Michelle Clark
OL,12,Ffrom Kent, decorate their house with
OL,13,Fhundreds of thousands of Christmas
OL,14,Flights in memory of their son Jack who
OL,15,Fwas born premature.
OL,17,FTheir enchanting light displays have
OL,18,Fhelped raise more than #50,000 for
OL,19,Fvarious children's charities.
