OL,4,Cmemory of son raises thousands for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FIt's become a bit of a festive
OL,8,Ftradition for many to visit the Clark
OL,9,Ffamily in Boughton-under Blean.
OL,11,FOver the last few years, the family
OL,12,Fhave built up a collection of more
OL,13,Fthan 100,000 lights.
OL,15,FIt's their way to remember their son
OL,16,FJack, who died at just 2 weeks old
OL,17,Fafter being born premature in 2002.
