OL,4,Cmemory of son raises thousands for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FAs part of the huge display, they've
OL,8,Fincluded a memory tree, so the
OL,9,Fcommunity can remember their loved
OL,10,Fones too.
OL,12,FSpeaking about the death of her son
OL,13,FJack, Michelle Clark said: "Over time
OL,14,Fyou want to celebrate his life, not
OL,15,Fgrieve it.
OL,17,F"So we started off with little
OL,18,Fthings...."
