OL,4,Cmemory of son raises thousands for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"We started off with a candle for his
OL,8,Fbirthday," Ross Clark added. "And with
OL,9,Fthe light of that candle we started
OL,10,Fputting lights up around the door,
OL,11,Fthen around the windows.
OL,13,F"Since then it's just progressed and
OL,14,Fprogressed."
OL,16,FEvery year the couple choose a
OL,17,Fdifferent children's charity to
OL,18,Ffundraise for.
