OL,3,CCouple's dazzling Christmas lights in
OL,4,Cmemory of son raises thousands for
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FLast year's recipient was the Oliver
OL,8,FFisher Trust - a neonatal unit based
OL,9,Fat Medway Maritime Hospital, that
OL,10,Fcares for the most vulnerable babies.
OL,12,FHannah Grout from the charity said:
OL,13,F"As a small local charity, local
OL,14,Fsupport means the world to us, and
OL,15,Fpeople like the Clarks make all the
OL,16,Fdifference.
OL,18,F"The money that the Clarks raised went
OL,19,Fdirectly to fund oxygenation modules
OL,20,Fto go on our breathing machines which
OL,21,Fcost #14,000.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
